OL,7,FSpeaking during court proceedings, Mr
OL,8,FSchiavone said: "The Welsh language is
OL,9,Fan official and equal language in
OL,10,FWales and we as Welsh speakers have
OL,11,Frights according to the law, and in
OL,12,Fprinciple, that should be respected.
OL,13,FThe request for a Parking Charge
OL,14,FNotice in Welsh or bilingually is
OL,15,Freasonable and practical. It would
OL,16,Fhave cost around #60 to translate."
