OL,7,FHe added: "This case could have been
OL,8,Fresolved very easily and very quickly
OL,9,Fby providing a Welsh or bilingual
OL,10,FParking Charge Notice. Does not doing
OL,11,Fso show prejudice against the Welsh
OL,12,Flanguage? In my opinion, it does."
OL,14,FThe first two cases against the Welsh
OL,15,Flanguage campaigner were thrown out
OL,16,Fover technical issues but One Parking
OL,17,FSolution won an appeal earlier this
OL,18,Fyear to continue prosecuting Mr
OL,19,FSchiavone.
