OL,7,FHe said they sent another letter with
OL,8,Fadditional costs of more than #4,000
OL,9,Ftwo days before this week's hearing.
OL,11,FJudge Lowri Williams said Mr Schiavone
OL,12,Fhad behaved in an "honest, principled"
OL,13,Fway and had shown "unwavering
OL,14,Fdedication to the Welsh language and
OL,15,Fthe cause for the language."
OL,17,FHowever, she said the parking company
OL,18,Fis not legally required to provide a
OL,19,FWelsh language version of the parking
OL,20,Fticket.
